adline6",{"type":173,"tag":305,"props":444,"children":445},{"style":333},[446],{"type":186,"value":360},{"type":173,"tag":305,"props":448,"children":450},{"class":307,"line":449},6,[451,456],{"type":173,"tag":305,"props":452,"children":453},{"style":318},[454],{"type":186,"value":455},"  )",{"type":173,"tag":305,"props":457,"children":458},{"style":333},[459],{"type":186,"value":360},{"type":173,"tag":305,"props":461,"children":463},{"class":307,"line":462},7,[464,469],{"type":173,"tag":305,"props":465,"children":466},{"style":318},[467],{"type":186,"value":468},")",{"type":173,"tag":305,"props":470,"children":471},{"style":333},[472],{"type":186,"value":473},";\n",{"type":173,"tag":200,"props":475,"children":476},{},[477],{"type":186,"value":478},"大部分跨平台框架使用 JS 作为基于 Java 的安卓以及基于 OC 的 iOS 的系统 UI 库的中间层，以及 UI 与 app logic 大量交互，拖累的性能。在 Flutter 中，Dart 代码最终被编译为 native 代码，直接交由 Skia 绘制。这就意味着没有中间层通讯以及 JS 缓慢速度带来的性能损耗。",{"type":173,"tag":200,"props":480,"children":481},{},[482],{"type":173,"tag":218,"props":483,"children":484},{},[485],{"type":186,"value":486},"Cross-platform frameworks typically work by creating an abstraction layer over the underlying native Android and iOS UI libraries, attempting to smooth out the inconsistencies of each platform representation. App code is often written in an interpreted language like JavaScript, which must in turn interact with the Java-based Android or Objective-C-based iOS system libraries to display UI.",{"type":173,"tag":200,"props":488,"children":489},{},[490],{"type":173,"tag":204,"props":491,"children":494},{"alt":492,"src":493},"what's render means in flutter","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20220615164637.png",[],{"type":173,"tag":200,"props":496,"children":497},{},[498],{"type":186,"value":499},"Layouts 时，依据深度优先策略把 constraints（min size、max size）自根像叶传递，相反地，实际的元素尺寸信息由叶向根传递。这有点类似某个浏览器中的布局算法？",{"type":173,"tag":200,"props":501,"children":502},{},[503],{"type":173,"tag":204,"props":504,"children":507},{"alt":505,"src":506},"from widgets to element tree, to render tree","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20220615164604.png",[],{"type":173,"tag":200,"props":509,"children":510},{},[511],{"type":186,"value":512},"事件不是 Dart 层处理，最终还是交给 Embedded 层处理，为什么要优于“跨平台的框架”？",{"type":173,"tag":200,"props":514,"children":515},{},[516],{"type":173,"tag":218,"props":517,"children":518},{},[519],{"type":186,"value":520},"When you start a Flutter app, the embedder provides the entrypoint, initializes the Flutter engine, obtains threads for UI and rastering, and creates a texture that Flutter can write to. The embedder is also responsible for the app lifecycle, including input gestures (such as mouse, keyboard, touch), window sizing, thread management, and platform messages.",{"type":173,"tag":200,"props":522,"children":523},{},[524],{"type":186,"value":525},"Skia 对接的是 iOS 或 macOS 的 UIViewController 和 NSViewController，安卓的 Activity，以及 Windows 的 ANGLE。这些平台的绘图库（？）直接和驱动打交道（？）。",{"type":173,"tag":200,"props":527,"children":528},{},[529],{"type":186,"value":530},"... 跳过“集成其它代码”部分",{"type":173,"tag":200,"props":532,"children":533},{},[534],{"type":186,"value":535},"Flutter 如果要在 Web 端用 WebGL 绘制，需要引入编译为 WASM 的 Skia 引擎。",{"type":173,"tag":200,"props":537,"children":538},{},[539],{"type":173,"tag":204,"props":540,"children":543},{"alt":541,"src":542},"flutter web support","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20220615164818.png?type=win11-square",[],{"type":173,"tag":545,"props":546,"children":547},"style",{},[548],{"type":186,"value":549},"html .light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html.light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var